version_description:
• Instantly remove/extract vocals, drums, piano, guitar, and other instruments from any song
• Smart Metronome: automatically generates click tracks matching the song tempo (best for drummers and musicians who dreamed of having a metronome built-in in any song)
• Pitch shifting: transpose songs to any key in real-time (best for singers, karaoke enthusiasts, and instrumentists).
• AI Chord detection: detect, visualize, and transpose Chords in real-time using Artificial Intelligence (guitar, bass, piano, and any other instrument player can follow chord progressions of their favorite music).

-New: click track export.
-bug fixes
